nodes.text: "Wicket Unleashed" is an article by Scott Chernoff that appeared in Star Wars Insider 31. It is based on an interview with actor Warwick Davis, who discusses his work on Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, Return of the Ewok, and Willow. The article also features a portrait of Wicket by Tsuneo Sanda.
A later article titled "Meet Wicket!" is based on "Wicket Unleashed."
